 restores of that data.

Package: zarafa-multiserver
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Section: non-free/mail
Conflicts: zarafa-licensed (<< 7.2)
Replaces: zarafa-licensed (<< 7.2)
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
 zarafa-server (= ${binary:Version}),
 zarafa-client (= ${binary:Version}),
 zarafa-licensed (= ${binary:Version}),
 python-mapi (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Multiserver LDAP plugin and tools
 Adds the ldapms plugin possebility to server setups for multiserver
 setups using LDAP or ADS. Users may be moved to different servers
 using the provided zarafa-msr python script.

