Package: zarafa-ws
Architecture: any
Section: non-free/mail
Depends: python-mapi (>= 7.2),
 zarafa-contacts (>= 7.2),
 python-flask,
 python-dateutil,
 python-openssl,
 zarafa-common (>= 7.2)
Description: The Zarafa implementation of the Exchange Web Services protocol
 This allows a broad scala of mail, contact and calendar clients that
 support EWS to connect with Zarafa without modification or additional
 configuration.
